text: Justín Javorek (14 September 1936 – 15 September 2021) was a Slovak football coach and goalkeeper. He played for the Czechoslovakia national team. From 1959 until 1969, he played for Inter Bratislava. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Slovak sportspeople Category:Football managers Category:Czechoslovak footballers
